title: Psychotropic substances recovered at Oman’s Muscat Airport from Asian men, womanTravelandtourworld.com
text:
Psychotropic Substances Recovered at Oman’s Muscat Airport from Asian men, woman
The Omani Customs Officers at Muscat International Airport managed to foil three attempts to smuggle 520 tablets of Tramadol by a woman arriving from an Asian country.
Further, an Asian national tried to smuggle 249 tablets of clonazepam, 270 tablets of diazepam in addition to 100 tablets of Tramadol by another Asian man.
The accused were referred to the Public Prosecution for further legal action against them.
